            <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-section">
                <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-dark mb-4 font-minecraft text-primary">留言板</h2>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">有什么Minecraft的技巧或建议？欢迎在这里交流</p>
